<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/645600-before-reading-it-i-thought-the-title">Before reading it, I thought the title implied there would be some issue about what to do with Angela&#39;s ashes. But it has nothing to do with that, so why is it titled &quot;Angela&#39;s Ashes&quot;?</a>
</div>
