<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/5952026-jennifer">Jennifer</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Have you read the whole book? Angela often stares into, and stirs, the gray ashes of the fireplace. It seems that the title has a metaphoric meaning..<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Have you read the whole book? Angela often stares into, and stirs, the gray ashes of the fireplace. It seems that the title has a metaphoric meaning...the ashes of a former life, or a life that has burned out, much like those mentioned in the Shinedown song 45: "I'm swimming through the ashes of another life"<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
