          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/166376-david?shelf=hideously-vile-protagonists">hideously-vile-protagonists</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/166376-david?shelf=mind-numbingly-boring">mind-numbingly-boring</a>, 
